pages.text:
Welcome to your ultimate waterfront paradise! Skipper's Dockside, Key Largo's oceanside oasis at Mile Marker 100, offers guests a comfortable portal to a time when life was simpler. Visitors enjoy a peek into the past as they make their turn onto Caribbean Drive; the exterior features an old-fashioned Ice House followed by a 1940's original filling station to assist in one's time travel journey.
Visitors might find themselves turned around as they venture inside the exotic fantasyland, Key Largo's essential destination, complete with staff dedicated to providing friendly service and a delicious mixture of offbeat ingredients and culinary tradition. Be prepared for some of Florida's freshest seafood around-local ingredients, fresh off the boat, soul food-High Quality Comfort Food.
Relaxed locals and paradise-minded vacationers are invited to experience Skipper's Dockside's endless signature cocktails, as well as, dozens of classic libations, using only the freshest juices, fruits, purees and hand-picked herbs. Rich, Vibrant, Unique-Skipper's Culinary Approach to the Art of a Cocktail.
And what better place to sip a tasty tropical drink than the spacious outdoor tiki bar perfectly situated for enjoying gorgeous marina views while boaters pull up dockside for exceptionally refreshing cocktails. Perfectly executed tiki classics, the bar offers a dizzying array of historic concoctions, complemented by Skipper's handcrafted highlights that are sure to impress tiki aficionados and tourists alike.
To top off this one-of-a-kind "adult playground," Skipper's offers live entertainment, indoor sports and interactive games; as well as, an over-sized media wall ideal for catching all your favorite sports games.
